on.%20The%20minutes%20of%20the%20cabinet%20meeting%20stated%20that%20Bihar%20has%2094%20lakh%20families%20living%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%20who%20have%20to%20be%20paid%20Rs%202%20lakh%20each%20in%20installments%20to%20get%20employment%2C%2063%2C850%20landless%20families%20to%20be%20paid%20Rs%201%20lakh%20each%20to%20buy%20land%2C%20and%20Rs%201.20%20lakh%20each%20to%20build%20houses.%20These%20expenses%20require%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20crore%20for%20which%20the%20Special%20Category%20Status%20to%20the%20state%20is%20required%2C%20he%20added.%20Besides%2C%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20raised%20reservation%20in%20the%20Ninth%20Schedule%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20would%20give%20Bihar%20immunity%20from%20legal%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbihar-extends-caste-based-reservation-from-50-percent-to-65-percent%5C%22%3EBihar%20Passes%20Bills%20Raising%20Caste-Based%20Quota%20From%2050%25%20To%2065%25%2C%20Taking%20Total%20Reservation%20to%2075%25%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20question%20arises%20whether%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20would%20accept%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20demand.%20Going%20by%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20of%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)-Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal-Congress-Left%20parties%20and%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%2C%20it%20is%20hardly%20likely%20that%20the%20Centre%20will%20yield%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20wishes.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20rejected%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20national%20caste%20census%20over%20two%20years%20ago.%20He%20has%20not%20granted%20Rs%201.20%20lakh%20crore%20of%20special%20packages%20that%20he%20had%20promised%20at%20his%20election%20meeting%20at%20Arra%20during%20the%202015%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20sympathisers%20of%20the%20BJP%20challenged%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20caste%20survey%20in%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20And%20the%20solicitor%20general%20of%20India%20opposed%20it%20in%20the%20apex%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20Union%20government%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20concede%20to%20the%20demand%20has%20become%20obvious%20with%20the%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20were%20ministers%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20Congress%20ruled%20India%20for%2075%20years.%20But%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20consider%20Bihar%20for%20Special%20Category%20Status.%20Now%2C%20the%2014th%20and%2015th%20Finance%20Commissions%20have%20said%20that%20no%20state%20would%20be%20given%20Special%20Category%20Status%20any%20longer.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20granted%20Rs%201.50%20lakh%20crore%20to%20Bihar%20as%20special%20financial%20assistance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPot%20boiling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20buoyed%20up%20by%20the%20response%20to%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20decided%20to%20get%20his%20cadres%20to%20hit%20the%20streets%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20Mahagathbandhan%20in%20the%20state%20and%20of%20the%20India%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20at%20the%20national%20level%20%E2%80%93%20staged%20demonstrations%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20on%20Friday%20to%20press%20for%20the%20Special%20Category%20Status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20assembly%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20will%20be%20known%20on%20December%203%2C%20but%20reports%20suggest%20that%20the%20caste%20survey%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20a%20strong%20impact%20on%20the%20electorate%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20promised%20a%20similar%20survey%20and%20proportionate%20participation%20of%20the%20marginalised%20communities%20in%20governance%20in%20every%20election%20meeting%20he%20has%20addressed.%20It%E2%80%99s%20obvious%20that%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20which%20have%20largely%20supported%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20caste%20survey%20%E2%80%93%20will%20make%20what%20they%20describe%20as%20a%20panacea%20to%20large-scale%20unemployment%20among%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20the%20main%20issue%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20who%20are%20working%20in%20harmony%2C%20are%2C%20apparently%2C%20aware%20that%20their%20moves%20have%20given%20a%20template%20to%20other%20parties%20including%20the%20Congress%20to%20fight%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20against%20the%20BJP.%20So%2C%20even%20if%20the%20BJP%20concedes%20to%20their%20demands%2C%20they%20would%20use%20the%20caste%20survey%20followed%20by%20the%20appointment%20of%201.20%20lakh%20teachers%20to%20keep%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19162700%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-02-22-at-11.12.03.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19162700%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-02-22-at-11.12.03.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19162700%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-02-22-at-11.12.03-300x163.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19162700%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-02-22-at-11.12.03-1024x556.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-658959%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22652%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20a%20BJP%20flag.%20Photo%3A%20Ismat%20Ara%2F%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20largely%20capable%20of%20doing%20it%20because%20of%20their%20mass%20base%20among%20the%20people.%20The%20RJD%20has%20a%20huge%20network%20of%20cadre%2C%20mostly%20comprising%20the%20backward%20classes%20in%20Bihar%20hinterlands.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20decided%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Eyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20hinterlands%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20to%20follow%20up%20on%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20development%20work%20at%20the%20ground%20level%20and%20know%20the%20response%20of%20the%20people.%20The%20BJP%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20clue%20to%20counter%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20moves%2C%20making%20an%20impact%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20at%20least%2C%20at%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnine-reasons-why-the-bihar-caste-census-could-shake-up-national-politics%5C%22%3ENine%20Reasons%20Why%20Numbers%20Revealed%20by%20Bihar%20Caste%20Census%20Could%20Shake%20Up%20National%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBihar%20model%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20Nitish%20has%20done%20all%20these%20things%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20without%20any%20planning%20and%20thinking.%20Prior%20to%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20dumping%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%202022%20and%20joining%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20of%20course%2C%20inspired%20by%20his%20father%20Lalu%2C%20had%20been%20demanding%20the%20caste%20census.%20He%20had%20promised%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth%20during%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections.%20Nitish%20and%20Tejashwi%20were%20united%20on%20these%20issues%20before%20joining%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20they%20came%20to%20power%2C%20they%20aggressively%20embarked%20on%20giving%20employment%20and%20carrying%20out%20the%20caste%20survey.%20On%20October%202%2C%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20released%20the%20figures%20of%20various%20castes%20in%20the%20state.%20On%20November%202%2C%20Nitish%2C%20Tejaswhi%20and%20other%20ministers%20distributed%20letters%20of%20appointment%20to%20as%20many%20as%201.20%20lakh%20newly%20recruited%20teachers%20in%20one%20day.%20In%20total%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20has%20given%20jobs%20to%20about%20four%20lakh%20unemployed%20youth%20since%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20came%20to%20power%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20government%20has%20planned%20for%20five%20years%20to%20address%20the%20challenges%20thrown%20by%20the%20caste%20survey%2C%20which%20primarily%20includes%20employment%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20population%20of%20the%20castes%20concerned%2C%20housing%2C%20land%2C%20and%20integration%20of%20marginalised%20sections%20in%20the%20governance%20apparatus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20all%20real%20issues%2C%20considered%20to%20be%20an%20antidote%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20the%20mainstay%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics.%20At%20the%20level%20of%20working%20out%20on%20seat%20adjustment%2C%20the%20INDIA%20partners%20are%20still%20far%20away.%20But%20they%20appear%20to%20have%20found%20common%20ground%20on%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20Bihar%20model%2C%20making%20them%20their%20central%20focus%20for%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700825210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07214142%2FF-AjAdfbYAA6UOc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-nitish-kumar-is-keeping-the-issue-of-bihar-caste-survey-alive%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recent%20decision%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Cabinet%20to%20demand%20the%20Centre%20to%20incorporate