rkers%20on%20a%20picket%20line%20outside%20the%20Coventry%20warehouse.%3Cp%3EJacob%20King%2FPA%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Black%20Friday%20is%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20busiest%20shopping%20days%2C%20an%20Amazon%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20action%20would%20cause%20%26quot%3Bzero%20disruption%20to%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20employs%20about%2075%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20but%20in%20the%20past%20year%20has%20been%20embroiled%20in%20an%20ongoing%20dispute%20over%20pay%20and%20conditions.%20At%20the%20Coventry%20warehouse%2C%20GMB%20membership%20has%20increased%20fivefold%20in%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2Fnov%2F19%2Fblack-friday-strike-could-mark-the-beginning-of-the-end-for-amazons-war-on-unions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Amazon%20announced%20a%20wage%20increase%20which%20it%20said%20would%20cost%20%24213%20million%20(%C2%A3170%20million).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3EBy%20April%202024%2C%20our%20minimum%20starting%20pay%20will%20have%20increased%20to%20%C2%A312.30%20and%20%C2%A313%20per%20hour%20depending%20on%20location%20%E2%80%93%20that's%20a%2020%25%20increase%20over%20two%20years%20and%2050%25%20since%202018%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20said%20pay%20was%20already%20above%20the%20UK's%20National%20Living%20Wage%20rate%20and%20that%20it%20offered%20employees%20a%20range%20of%20benefits%2C%20career%20opportunities%20and%20a%20good%20working%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20minimum%20wage%20has%20just%20been%20increased%20from%20%2413.08%20to%20%2414.36%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-workers-strikes-protests-blac