t%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BWe're%20having%20a%20party%20and%20we%20want%20our%20home%20to%20look%20really%20nice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20Christmas%20stuff%2C%20so%20it%20was%20just%20natural%20to%20me%20that%20the%20clients%20I%20helped%20during%20the%20year%20also%20wanted%20me%20to%20up%20their%20Christmas%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20would%20love%20to%20do%20it%20year%20round%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20that%20would%20make%20sense%20logistically.%20The%20demand%20for%20Christmas%2C%20at%20least%20around%20here%2C%20starts%20in%20October%20and%20ends%20in%20early%20December%2C%20if%20not%20sooner.%20It's%20actually%20a%20very%20small%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Courtney%20Warren's%20holiday%20designs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e39f84ca513d8242db3cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECourtney%20Warren's%20holiday%20designs%2C%20including%20a%20hot-chocolate%20station.%3Cp%3EJarrod%20Estes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20certain%20design%20style.%20I%20like%20vintage%20and%20antique%20pieces%2C%20and%20I%20mix%20them%20with%20new%20items%20to%20keep%20the%20home%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20magazine%20spreads%20and%20I'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcourtneywarrenhome%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eactive%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20business%20also%20spreads%20by%20word%20of%20mouth%20and%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20repeat%20clients.%20During%20the%20Christmas%20holiday%20season%2C%20I%20get%20about%2050%20to%2060%20emails%20and%20phone%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20years%2C%20I've%20had%2020%20clients%20and%20then%20others%2C%20I've%20had%20five%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20depends%20on%20how%20big%20the%20projects%20are.%20For%20some%20people%2C%20I%20design%20just