0hospitality%20industry.%20He%20became%20interested%20in%20politics%20early%20and%20his%20star%20rose%20quickly%20to%20California%20governor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgavin-newsom-career-timeline%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPushing%20In%20Just%20Two%20More%20Pipes%20May%20Get%20Us%20To%20Trapped%20Workers%26quot%3B%3A%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnly%2010-12%20metres%20of%20drilling%20is%20left%20for%20rescuers%20to%20reach%20the%2041%20construction%20workers%20trapped%20in%20the%20Uttarakhand%20tunnel%20for%20the%2013th%20day%20now%2C%20but%20giving%20a%20timeframe%20for%20the%20rescue%20is%20difficult%20because%20unexpected%20hurdles%20have%20been%20delaying%20the%20work%2C%20senior%20officials%20said%20on%20Friday%20afternoon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20be%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%20after%20all%2C%20however%2C%20as%20ground%20penetrating%20radar%20has%20revealed%20that%20there%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20no%20major%20metal%20obstacles%20for%20the%20next%20five%20metres%20that%20will%20be%20drilled%20in%20the%20next%20few%20hours.%20The%20officials%20also%20said%20that%2C%20if%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20pushing%20in%20two%20more%20pipes%20may%20be%20enough%20to%20reach%20the%20labourers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Additional%20Secretary%20Technical%2C%20Road%20and%20Transport%2C%20Mahmood%20Ahmed%20and%20Uttarakhand%20Secretary%20Neeraj%20Khairwal%2C%20who%20is%20the%20nodal%20officer%20for%20the%20rescue%20operation%2C%20said%20the%20auger%20machine%20hit%20a%20metal%20pipe%20on%20Thursday%20evening%20which%20wrapped%20itself%20around%20the%20drilling%20blades.%20They%20said%20many%20hours%20had%20to%20be%20spent%20repairing%20the%20machine's%20blades%2C%20strengthening%20the%20platform%20on%20which%20the%20machine%20is%20operating%20and%20removing%20the%20metal%20girders%20and%20pipes%20which%20were%20obstructing%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ahmed%20said%20that%2C%20before%20drilling%20resumes%2C%20some%20welding%20will%20need%20to%20be%20done%2C%20which%20will%20take%20about%20two%20hours.%20He%20explained%20that%20the%20welding%20process%20is%20a%20complicated%20one%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20carefully%20so%20that%20the%20area%20being%20welded%20stays%20strong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20one%20reason%20for%20the%20delay%2C%20Mr%20Khairwal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSince%204%20pm%20yesterday%20to%20now%2C%20time%20was%20spent%20strengthening%20the%20platform%2C%20which%20had%20moved.%20The%20mouth%20of%20one%20of%20the%20800%20mm%20pipes%20that%20had%20been%20pushed%20in%20by%20us%20had%20narrowed%20and%20we%20actually%20had%20to%20cut%20about%201.2%20metres%20of%20it.%20Three%20metres%20of%20pipe%20had%20been%20pushed%20in%20yesterday%20in%20addition%20to%20the%2045%20metres%20before%2C%20but%201.2%20metres%20of%20this%20had%20to%20be%20cut%20because%20the%20auger%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20proceed%20further.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20distance%20covered%20by%20the%20pipes%20is%20currently%2046.8%20metres%20because%201.2%20metres%20had%20to%20be%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khairwal%20said%20cutting%20the%20pipe%20as%20well%20as%20vertical%20pipes%20from%20the%20tunnel's%20ceiling%20that%20were%20obstructing%20the%20drill%20took%20seven%20to%20eight%20hours%20and%20while%20people%20thought%20that%20the%20auger%20machine%20had%20broken%20down%2C%20that%20was%20not%20the%20case.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20a%20team%20of%20ground%20penetrating%20radar%20experts%20was%20called%20in%20and%20one%20of%20their%20men%20took%2045%20minutes%20to%20travel%20inside%20the%20pipes%20for%2045%20metres%20and%20take%20their%20measuring%20machine%20inside.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20narrowing%20of%20the%20end%20of%20the%20pipe%20meant%20they%20could%20not%20say%20this%20with%20100%25%20accuracy%20but%20what%20they%20are%20expecting%20is%20that%20there%20is%20no%20continuous%20metal%20object%2C%20like%20girders%2C%20pipes%20and%20metal%20plates%2C%20in%20the%20next%205.4%20metres.%20They%20have%20pointed%20out%20some%20other%20hurdles%2C%20but%20this%20is%20good%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20700%20mm%20auger%20is%20going%20to%20be%20used%20now%20that%20the%20pipe%20has%20been%20cut%2C%20Mr%20Khairwal%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20hope%20is%20that%20the%20work%20will%20be%20completed%20at%20the%20earliest.%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20hour%20of%20drilling%20after%20the%20welding%20is%20done%20will%20be%20critical%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ahmed%20said%2C%20if%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20pushing%20in%20and%20welding%20two%20pipes%20with%20a%20length%20of%206%20metres%20each%20should%20be%20enough%20to%20%26quot%3Bbreak%20through%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20workers%20but%20this%20is%20an%20assumption%20based%20on%20their%20assessments.%20He%20cautioned%2C%20however%2C%20that%20obstacles%20and%20hurdles%20can%20still%20appear%20at%20any%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20teams%20could%20reach%20the%20workers%20by%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20the%20official%20said%20it%20could%20happen%20even%20sooner%20if%20everything%20goes%20smoothly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20under-construction%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarkashi%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20project%2C%20a%20national%20infrastructure%20initiative%20to%20enhance%20connectivity%20to%20the%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20of%20Badrinath%2C%20Kedarnath%2C%20Gangotri%2C%20and%20Yamunotri.%20The%20labourers%20got%20trapped%20when%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20tunnel%20had%20collapsed%20on%20November%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700823780000%2C%22vis