ompany%20for%20a%20fortnight%2C%20and%20forcing%20him%20to%20apologise%20by%20holding%20her%20footwear%20in%20his%20mouth%20for%20demanding%20salary%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20Nilesh%20Dalsaniya%2C%20lodged%20a%20complaint%2C%20based%20on%20which%20Morbi%20city's%20'A'%20division%20police%20on%20Thursday%20registered%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20the%20woman%2C%20identified%20as%20Vibhuti%20Patel%20aka%20Raniba%2C%20and%20others%20including%20her%20brother%20Om%20Patel%20and%20manager%20Parikshit%2C%20said%20Pratipalsinh%20Zala%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SC%2FST%20Cell).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVibhuti%20Patel%20is%20the%20owner%20of%20Raniba%20Industries%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20which%20has%20an%20office%20in%20a%20commercial%20complex%20at%20Ravapar%20Crossroad.%20In%20the%20beginning%20of%20October%2C%20she%20hired%20Dalsaniya%2C%20who%20is%20into%20tiles%20marketing%2C%20on%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%2C%20the%20FIR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20October%2018%2C%20she%20suddenly%20sacked%20him.%20When%20Dalsaniya%20sought%20his%20salary%20for%2016%20days%20that%20he%20worked%20in%20the%20company%2C%20Patel%20did%20not%20give%20a%20clear%20answer%20and%20then%20stopped%20responding%20to%20his%20calls%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Dalsaniya%2C%20his%20brother%20Mehul%20and%20neighbour%20Bhavesh%20went%20to%20Patel's%20office%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20the%20businesswoman's%20brother%20Om%20Patel%20reached%20the%20place%20with%20his%20accomplices%20and%20started%20assaulting%20the%20trio%2C%26quot%3B%20Zala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVibhuti%20Patel%20also%20slapped%20and%20dragged%20him%20to%20the%20terrace%20of%20the%20commercial%20complex%2C%20the%20FIR%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20including%20Parikshit%20Patel%2C%20Om%20Patel%20and%20six%20to%20seven%20unidentified%20men%2C%20beat%20him%20with%20belts%20and%20also%20kicked%20and%20punched%20him%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20alleged%20that%20Vibhuti%20Patel%20forced%20him%20to%20take%20her%20footwear%20in%20his%20mouth%20and%20made%20him%20apologise%20for%20demanding%20salary.%20She%20also%20threatened%20to%20get%20him%20killed%20if%20he%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20Ravapar%20Crossroad%20area%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20shot%20a%20video%20and%20forced%20him%20to%20say%20that%20he%20came%20to%20Vibhuti's%20office%20to%20extort%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%2C%20the%20accused%20are%20seen%20forcing%20the%20Dalit%20man%20to%20apologise%20to%20the%20woman%20employer%20for%20seeking%20his%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20home%2C%20the%20Dalit%20man%20was%20taken%20to%20Morbi%20civil%20hospital%20where%20he%20is%20currently%20undergoing%20treatment%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20accused%20were%20booked%20on%20the%20charges%20of%20assault%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20rioting%20and%20under%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20Zala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20into%20the%20case%20is%20underway%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20no%20arrest%20has%20been%20made%20yet.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700822340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fb6lvne1c_vibhuti-patel-owner-of-raniba-industries-assaults-dalit-man-insta-photo_625x300_24_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-employer-puts-footwear-in-dalit-mans-mouth-makes-him-say-sorry-o