x.police.uk%2Fnews%2Fessex%2Fnews%2Fnews%2F2023%2Fnovember%2Fbasildon-organised-drug-dealer-caught-after-posting-selfie-on-encrypted-chat%2F%5C%22%3EEssex%20Police%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Stirling%20was%20found%20on%20the%20vessel%20and%20was%20immediately%20recognised%20by%20officers.%20Also%20seized%20from%20the%20boat%20were%20a%20suspected%20encrypted%20mobile%20device%2C%20cannabis%2C%20hundreds%20of%20tablets%2C%20and%20a%20signal%20jammer%20device.%20A%20vehicle%20attributed%20to%20Stirling%20was%20traced%20to%20two%20self-storage%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20one%20of%20the%20units%2C%20officers%20discovered%20more%20than%20ten%20million%20tablets%2C%20suspected%20to%20be%20diazepam%20due%20to%20the%20wrapping%20but%20later%20found%20to%20be%20an%20antihistamine%20following%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20EncroChat%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Essex%20Police%2C%20EncroChat%20offered%20a%20secure%20mobile%20phone%20instant%20messaging%20service%20with%2060%2C000%20users%20worldwide%20and%20around%2010%2C000%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20use%20was%20for%20coordinating%20and%20planning%20criminal%20activities%2C%20including%20the%20distribution%20of%20illicit%20commodities%20and%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202016%2C%20international%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20have%20worked%20together%20to%20target%20EncroChat%2C%20and%20in%202020%2C%20agencies%20in%20France%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20infiltrated%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intelligence%20gleaned%20through%20this%20operation%20was%20then%20shared%20via%20Europol%20with%20national%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700822160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fiq6h0a6_darren-stirling-has-been-jailed-for-18-years_625x300_24_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fuk-drug-dealer-caught-after-sharing-to