https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fananya-panday-pens-a-heartfelt-note-for-gauri-khan-as-she-decorates-her-first-home-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F105473635.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Planes%20Losing%20GPS%20Signal%20Over%20Middle-East%2C%20Indian%20Regulator%20Flags%20Threat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EConcerned%20over%20reports%20that%20civilian%20aircrafts%20may%20sometimes%20be%20flying%20blind%20over%20parts%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20the%20civil%20aviation%20regulator%20DGCA%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory%20to%20all%20Indian%20airlines.%20There%20have%20been%20several%20reports%20in%20recent%20days%20that%20navigation%20systems%20of%20civilian%20aircrafts%20are%20being%20spoofed%20when%20they%20fly%20over%20parts%20of%20the%20Middle%20East.%20This%20is%20fast%20emerging%20as%20a%20major%20safety%20hazard%20and%20the%20DGCA%20advisory%20aims%20to%20alert%20airlines%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20threat%20and%20how%20to%20respond%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aviation%20industry%20is%20grappling%20with%20uncertainties%20due%20to%20new%20threats%20and%20reports%20of%20GNSS%20(Global%20Navigation%20Satellite%20System)%20jamming%20and%20spoofing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20circular%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20takes%20note%20of%20%26quot%3Bincreasing%20reports%20of%20GNSS%20interference%20over%20airspace%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20in%20the%20recent%20past%26quot%3B%20and%20calls%20for%20the%20development%20of%20contingency%20measures%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20jamming%20of%20navigation%20systems.%20The%20DGCA%20has%20also%20sought%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20threat%20monitoring%20and%20analysis%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20September%2C%20multiple%20commercial%20flights%20near%20Iran%20went%20off-course%20after%20their%20navigation%20systems%20went%20blind.%20One%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%20which%20fell%20victim%20to%20spoofing%2C%20ended%20up%20almost%20flying%20into%20Iranian%20airspace%20without%20permission.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20OpsGroup%2C%20a%20group%20of%20professional%20pilots%2C%20flight%20dispatchers%2C%20schedulers%2C%20and%20controllers%20have%20flagged%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Does%20The%20Spoofing%20Work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20planes%20flying%20over%20parts%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20initially%20receive%20a%20spoofed%20GPS%20signal.%20This%20signal%20is%20aimed%20at%20fooling%20the%20aircraft's%20in-built%20system%20into%20thinking%20that%20they%20are%20flying%20miles%20away%20from%20their%20intended%20route.%20The%20signal%20is%20often%20strong%20enough%20to%20compromise%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20aircraft's%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fekejbuuo_gps-spoofing_625x300_24_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20that%20within%20minutes%2C%20the%20inertial%20reference%20system%20(IRS)%20becomes%20unstable%20and%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20plane%20loses%20all%20navigation%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20Are%20The%20Areas%20Of%20Concern%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20area%20of%20concern%20is%20a%20busy%20airway%20in%20Northern%20Iraq%20and%20Azerbaijan%20with%20several%20incidents%20being%20reported%20near%20Erbil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Feicvi7n_gps-spoofing_625x300_24_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20September%2C%2012%20separate%20incidents%20had%20been%20reported%20with%20the%20latest%20one%20being%20reported%20near%20Ankara%2C%20Turkey%20on%20November%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20The%20Culprit%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20no%20one%20culprit%20has%20been%20identified%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20jamming%20and%20spoofing%20may%20be%20happening%20because%20of%20the%20deployment%20of%20military%20electronic%20warfare%20systems%20in%20areas%20where%20there%20is%20regional%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20The%20DGCA%20Circular%20Recommend%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGCA%20circular%20is%20based%20on%20recommendations%20of%20the%20committee%20for%20tackling%20the%20emerging%20threat%20considering%20the%20best%20practices%2C%20latest%20developments%2C%20and%20International%20Civil%20Aviation%20Organization%20(ICAO)%20guidance%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20provides%20comprehensive%20mitigation%20measures%20and%20action%20plans%20for%20aircraft%20operators%2C%20pilots%2C%20ANSP%2C%20and%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20which%20includes%20the%20development%20of%20contingency%20procedures%20in%20coordination%20with%20equipment%20manufacturers%2C%20and%20the%20assessment%20of%20operational%20risk%20by%20conducting%20a%20safety%20risk%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20provides%20a%20mechanism%20to%20establish%20a%20threat%20monitoring%20and%20analysis%20network%20in%20close%20coordination%20with%20DGCA%20for%20preventive%20as%20well%20as%20reactive%20threat%20monitoring%20and%20analysis%20of%20reports%20of%20GNSS%20interference%20to%20generate%20valuable%20insights%20with%20data%20and%20new%20developments%20so%20as%20to%20have%20robust%20and%20immediate%20threat%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700821980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fnpptv5u_cockpit_625x300_24_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fplanes-losing-gps-signa