hat%20there%20is%20a%20low%20risk%20to%20India%20from%20both%20the%20avian%20influenza%20cases%20reported%20from%20China%20as%20well%20as%20the%20clusters%20of%20respiratory%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20prepared%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20exigency%20that%20may%20emerge%20from%20the%20current%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20usual%20causes%20of%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20children%20have%20been%20implicated%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20identification%20of%20an%20unusual%20pathogen%20or%20any%20unexpected%20clinical%20manifestations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overall%20risk%20assessment%20by%20the%20WHO%20indicates%20a%20low%20probability%20of%20human-to-human%20spread%20and%20low%20case%20fatality%20rate%20among%20human%20cases%20of%20H9N2%20reported%20to%20the%20WHO%20so%20far.%20The%20need%20for%20strengthening%20surveillance%20among%20human%2C%20animal%20husbandry%2C%20and%20wildlife%20sectors%20and%20improving%20coordination%20was%20recognised.%20India%20is%20prepared%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20public%20health%20exigency%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20further%20added%20that%20India%20is%20embarking%20on%20a%20One%20Health%20approach%20to%20adopt%20a%20holistic%20and%20integrated%20roadmap%20towards%20solving%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20also%20been%20a%20significant%20overhaul%20of%20health%20infrastructure%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20COVID%20pandemic.%20PM-Ayushman%20Bharat%20Health%20Infrastructure%20Mission%20(PM-ABHIM)%20is%20developing%20capacities%20of%20health%20systems%20and%20institutions%20across%20the%20continuum%20of%20care%20at%20all%20levels%2C%20primary%2C%20secondary%2C%20and%20tertiary%2C%20to%20prepare%20health%20systems%20to%20respond%20effectively%20to%20current%20and%20future%20pandemics%20or%20disasters%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20preparedness%20against%20human%20cases%20of%20Avian%20Influenza%20in%20the%20country%20after%20China%20reported%20a%20human%20case%20of%20H9N2%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20mid-October%2C%20WHO%20has%20been%20monitoring%20data%20from%20Chinese%20surveillance%20systems%20showing%20an%20increase%20in%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20children%20in%20northern%20China%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20health%20agency%20announced%20late%20Wednesday%20it%20had%20made%20an%20official%20request%20to%20Beijing%20for%20more%20data%2C%20but%20the%20government%20offered%20no%20public%20comment%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700821140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fe8ul6shg_china-reuters_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-says-closely-monitoring-respiratory-illness-outbreak-in-china-4602378%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Health%20Ministry%20said%20it%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20outbreaks%20of%20H9N2%20(Avian%20influenza%20virus)%20cases%20and%20clusters%20of%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20children%20in%20northern%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-says-closely-monitoring-respiratory-illness-outbreak-in-china-4602378%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-says-closely-monitoring-respiratory-illness-outbreak-in-china-4602378%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-says-closely-monitoring-respiratory-illness-outbreak-in-china-4602378%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marrakech%20Film%20Fest%20Chief%20Talks%20This%20Year%E2%8