%20in%20the%20valley%20have%20dropped%20below%200%C2%B0C.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Kashmir%20requires%201800%20MW%20of%20power%20to%20maintain%20electricity%20supply%20for%2016%20hours%20a%20day.%20For%20round-the-clock%20supply%2C%202200%20to%202300%20MWs%20is%20required.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Power%20Development%20Department%20(PDD)%20this%20winter%20has%20only%20been%20able%20to%20produce%2050-100%20MWs%20a%20day%20as%20opposed%20to%20200-250%20MWs%20in%20the%20past.%20To%20meet%20the%20deficit%2C%20power%20was%20purchased%20from%20the%20Northern%20Grid%20and%20power%20cuts%20were%20reduced%20to%20six%20to%20four%20hours%20by%20previous%20regimes%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20PDD%20official%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fkashmirs-18-hour-power-cuts-are-collective-punishment-says-opposition%2Farticle67566514.ece%5C%22%3Ethis%20year%E2%80%99s%20production%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20prolonged%20dry%20spell%20in%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%20accompanied%20by%20freezing%20temperatures%20in%20November%20which%20further%20slowed%20down%20the%20waster%20discharge%20in%20rivers%20like%20the%20Jhelum.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20impacting%20the%20elderly%2C%20the%20power%20cuts%20are%20posing%20a%20significant%20challenge%20to%20chronic%20obstructive%20pulmonary%20disease%20(COPD)%20patients%2C%20whose%20numbers%20go%20up%20during%20the%20winters%2C%20the%20paper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%2C%20who%20is%20in%20his%2070s%2C%20is%20a%20COPD%20patient.%20We%20had%20to%20buy%20a%20generator%20so%20that%20his%20oxygen%20concentrator%20machine%20runs%20without%20disruptions.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20all%20families%20can%20afford%20generators.%20Prolonged%20power%20cuts%20are%20a%20death%20knell%20for%20such%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20Imtiyaz%20Khan%2C%20a%20showroom%20owner%20from%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20Lal%20Bazaar%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Students%20appearing%20for%20their%20year-end%20examinations%20are%20also%20facing%20great%20difficulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20government%20purchases%201150%20MWs%20but%20still%20falls%20short%20by%20650%20MWs%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20fix%20responsibility.%20Why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20officers%20raise%20an%20alarm%20about%20dip%20in%20water%20discharge%20and%20prepare%20a%20proposal%20to%20purchase%20from%20the%20Northern%20Grid.%20This%20crisis%20did%20not%20happen%20overnight.%20There%20was%20a%20prolonged%20dry%20spell%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20observe.%20If%20there%20was%20an%20elected%20government%20such%20a%20crisis%20would%20not%20have%20happened%20and%20the%20responsibility%20would%20have%20been%20fixed%2C%E2%80%9D%20J%26amp%3BK%20Apni%20Party%20president%20Altaf%20Bukhari%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fkashmirs-18-hour-power-cuts-are-collective-punishment-says-opposition%2Farticle67566514.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20collective%20punishment.%20The%20L-G%20should%20go%20to%20Delhi%20and%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20Centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bukhari%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Lieutenant%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20administration%20is%20said%20to%20have%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20purchase%20electricity%20from%20the%20Northern%20Grid%2C%20as%20hospitals%20are%20beginning%20to%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20power%20cut.%20However%2C%20the%20cost%20per%20unit%20at%20the%20Northern%20Grid%20at%20present%20is%20Rs%2042%20against%20Rs.%203-4%20being%20charged%20from%20consumers%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20leaders%20of%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20also%20held%20a%20street%20protest%20at%20the%20party%20headquarters%20in%20Srinagar%20over%20the%20power%20crisis%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fkashmirs-18-hour-power-cuts-are-collective-punishment-says-opposition%2Farticle67566514.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20public%20outcry%20against%20power%20cuts%2C%20divisional%20commissioner%2C%20Kashmir%2C%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Bidhuri%20said%20the%20situation%20is%20expected%20to%20improve%20within%20a%20week.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20power%20schedule%20announced%20earlier%20is%20not%20being%20adhered%20to%20as%20demand%20has%20abruptly%20gone%20up%20due%20to%20the%20early%20onset%20of%20winter.%20We%20are%20expecting%20an%20improvement%20in%20the%20power%20scenario%20as%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20and%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20have%20constituted%20a%20committee%20for%20power%20purchase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700815453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29165552%2FIMG_5033.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F16-hour-long-power-cuts-kashmir-faces-unprecedented-crisis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20an%20elected%20government%20such%20a%20crisis%20would%20not%20have%20happened%20and%20the%20responsibility%20would%20have%20been%20fixed%2C%26quot%3B%20J%26amp%3BK%20Apni%20Party%20president%20Altaf%20Bukhari%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F16-hour-long-power-cuts-kashmir-faces-unprecedented-crisis%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Deepfakes%2C%20IT%20Minister's%207-Day%20Deadline%20F