ke%20appointments%20based%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20LG%20(Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena)%20and%20CM%20(Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal)%20meet%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20responded%20and%20then%20observed%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20(but)%20last%20time%20we%20said%20that%2C%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20DERC%20(Delhi%20Electricity%20Regulatory%20Commission)%20Chairperson%2C%20they%20never%20agreed...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo...%20why%20doesn't%20LG%20and%20centre%20propose%20a%20panel%20of%20names%3F%20Ultimate%20choice%20will%20be%20from%20a%20panel%20made%20by%20you.%20You%20suggest%20a%20panel.%20Then%20they%20(the%20Delhi%20government)%20will%20pick%20up%20one%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20proposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20accepted%20this%20and%20said%20he%20would%20return%20with%20a%20shortlist%20as%20directed%2C%20but%20took%20a%20swipe%20on%20his%20way%20out%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B...(but)%20the%20officers%2C%20the%20way%20they're%20being%20treated%20-%20much%20is%20to%20be%20said%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20will%20I%20treat%3F%20I%20have%20no%20authority.%20All%20officers%20are%20under%20LG%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20shot%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20surrounding%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20whose%20son%20was%20linked%20to%20an%20alleged%20real%20estate%20scam%20in%20a%20news%20report%20published%20on%20November%209.%20On%20Wednesday%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20gave%20Mr%20Kumar%20relief%2C%20directing%20the%20news%20website%20to%20take%20down%20the%20article%20that%20was%20said%20to%20be%20defamatory%20of%20the%20current%20Delhi%20Chief%20Secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%2C%20in%20his%20plea%2C%20sought%20to%20take%20down%20the%20article%20as%20well%20as%20a%20direction%20to%20r