%20at%20Min%20Thar%20in%20that%20country%E2%80%99s%20Sagaing%20region%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbetween%20border%20pillar%20no%2090-91%20of%20Myanmar%20around%204%20am%20on%20November%2022.%E2%80%9D%20The%20border%20pillar%20is%20along%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Kamjong%20district%2C%20about%20120%20kms%20from%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2018903.8799615966!2d94.24269853047666!3d24.48122640473368!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x37499f9966106df3%253A0xb122d2d4a993790c!2sMin%2520Thar%252C%2520Myanmar%2520(Burma)!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1700807999499!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuperintendent%20of%20Police%20of%20Kamjong%2C%20P.%20Manjit%2C%20and%20OC%20Kasom%20Khullen%20Marchang%20Wungmahai%20and%20some%20villagers%20went%20across%20the%20(Myanmar)%20border%20to%20follow%20up%20the%20incident%20from%20Namlee%20side.%20There%20have%20been%20no%20latest%20reports%20of%20the%20team%20led%20by%20SP%20returning%20back%20to%20the%20border%20till%20late%20evening%20on%20Wednesday%20(November%2022).%20Namlee%20village%20in%20Maniour%E2%80%99s%20Kamjong%20district%20is%20close%20to%20the%20border%20pillars%2090-91.%20The%20report%20said%20villagers%20heard%20%E2%80%9Csounds%20of%20numerous%20bomb%20explosions%20across%20the%20border%20after%20the%20incident%20(that%20killed%20Naomram%20Naocha).%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20tried%20contacting%20the%20SP%20office%20at%20Kamjong%20but%20could%20not%20get%20a%20response.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMob%20storms%20hospital%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20another%20news%20report%20has%20stated%20that%20a%20Myanmarese%20man%20lost%20his%20life%20after%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(JNIMS)%20this%20November%2023.%20On%20getting%20to%20know%20that%20the%20man%20had%20been%20admitted%20in%20the%20hospital%20for%20treatment%2C%20a%20mob%20belonging%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%20stormed%20into%20the%20compound%20of%20the%20government-run%20hospital%20on%20November%2023%2C%20leading%20the%20state%20police%20to%20lob%20teargas%20at%20them%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmob-storms-imphal-hospital-treating-man-injured-myanmar-fighting-9040206%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmob-storms-imphal-hospital-treating-man-injured-myanmar-fighting-9040206%2F%5C%22%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20said%20the%20man%2C%20identified%20as%20Khoantum%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Thanan%2C%20in%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Sagaing%20region%2C%20died%20at%20the%20hospital%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%20of%20bullet%20injuries%20that%20he%20suffered%20during%20the%20fighting%20in%20Myanmar%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20news%20report%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mob%20had%20gathered%20at%20JNIMS%20due%20to%20a%20rumour%20that%20the%20man%20was%20a%20militant%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Myanmarese%20man%20was%20given%20first%20aid%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20that%20man%20the%20border%2C%20before%20being%20handedm%20over%20to%20the%20state%20police%20at%20around%203.55%20am%20on%20November%2023.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20that%2C%20they%20would%20have%20taken%20him%20to%20Imphal%20for%20further%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20security%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndian%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithin%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Community%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20(CoTU)%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%20has%20reimposed%20the%20blockade%20of%20the%20National%20Highways%202%20and%2037%20that%20pass%20by%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Kangpokpi%20district%2C%20located%20about%2045%20kms%20from%20Imphal.%20CoTU%20has%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20not%20ensuring%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20areas.%20The%20blockade%20of%20these%20highways%20typically%20chokes%20the%20supply%20of%20essentials%20to%20the%20valley%20areas%2C%20the%20home%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20which%20swells%20the%20animosity%20between%20the%20two%20clashing%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700810320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24124703%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-12.46.3.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-myanmar-meitei-kuki-chin%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20in%20the%20Imphal%20Free%20Press%20also%20said%20that%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20another%20valley-based%20(Meitei)%20underground%20outfit%20%E2%80%9Creportedly%20exchanged%20a%20gunfight%20with%20PDF%20at%20Thanan%20in%20Myanmar%20around%20noon.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-myanmar-meitei-kuki-chin%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20All%20About%20The%20Israel-Hamas%20Hostage%20Deal%20And%20Gaza%20Ceasefire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20Palestinian%20Islamist%20group%20Hamas%20will%20start%20a%20four-day%20truce%20on%20Friday%20morning%20with%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%20released%20later%20that%20day%2C%20mediators%20in%20Qatar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20details%20of%20the%20deal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20deal%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20a%20four-day%20truce%20so%20that%2050%20women%20and%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%2019%20taken%20hostage%20could%20be%20freed%20in%20return%20for%20150%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20teenagers%20in%20Israeli%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2050%20hostages%2C%20among%20about%20240%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20in%20their%20Oct.%207%20raid%20on%20Israel%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20released%20in%20batches%2C%20probably%20about%20a%20dozen%20a%20day%2C%20during%20the%20four-day%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20involved%20in%20the%20deal%20have%20described%20the%20break%20in%20hostilities%20%26quot%3Ba%20humanitarian%20pause%26quot%3B.%20The%20pause%20will%20be%20extended%20by%20a%20day%20for%20each%20additional%20batch%20of%2010%20hostages%20released%2C%20Israel%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20Israel%20had%20agreed%20to%20halt%20air%20traffic%20over%20the%20north%20of%20Gaza%20from%2010%20am%20(1.30%20pm%20IST)%20until%204%20pm%20(7.30%20pm%20IST)%20each%20day%20of%20the%20truce%20and%20to%20halt%20all%20air%20traffic%20over%20the%20south%20for%20the%20entire%20period.%20The%20group%20said%20Israel%20agreed%20not%20to%20attack%20or%20arrest%20anyone%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20people%20can%20move%20freely%20along%20Salah%20al-Din%20Street%2C%20the%20main%20road%20along%20which%20many%20Palestinians%20have%20fled%20northern%20Gaza%20where%20Israel%20launched%20its%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatar's%20chief%20negotiator%20in%20ceasefire%20talks%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20at%20the%20Foreign%20Ministry%20Mohammed%20Al-Khulaifi%2C%20said%20that%20under%20the%20deal%20there%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bno%20attack%20whatsoever.%20No%20military%20movements%2C%20no%20expansion%2C%20nothing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20did%20the%20deal%20start%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truce%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20started%20on%20Friday%20at%207%20am%20(10.30%20am%20IST)%2C%20with%20a%20first%20batch%20of%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20at%204%20pm%20(7.30%20pm)%2C%20a%20Qatari%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20lists%20of%20all%20civilians%20that%20would%20be%20released%20from%20Gaza%20had%20been%20agreed%20and%20said%20Qatar%20hoped%20to%20negotiate%20a%20subsequent%20agreement%20to%20release%20additional%20hostages%20from%20Gaza%20by%20the%20fourth%20day%20of%20the%20truce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20armed%20wing%20of%20Hamas%20confirmed%20the%200500%20GMT%20start%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20it%20be%20implemented%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20(ICRC)%20will%20work%20in%20Gaza%20to%20facilitate%20the%20release%20of%20the%20hostages%2C%20Qatar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hostages%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20transported%20through%20Egypt%2C%20the%20only%20country%20apart%20from%20Israel%20to%20share%20a%20border%20with%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20truce%2C%20trucks%20loaded%20with%20aid%20and%20fuel%20are%20expected%20to%20cross%20into%20Gaza%2C%20where%202.3%20million%20people%20have%20been%20running%20out%20of%20food%20and%20many%20hospitals%20have%20shut%20down%20in%20part%20because%20they%20no%20longer%20have%20fuel%20for%20their%20generators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas%20armed%20wing%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20200%20aid%20trucks%20and%20four%20fuel%20trucks%20would%20enter%20Gaza%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20operations%20room%20in%20Doha%20will%20monitor%20the%20truce%20and%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20and%20has%20direct%20lines%20of%20communication%20with%20Israel%2C%20the%20Hamas%20political%20office%20in%20Doha%20and%20ICRC%2C%20Qatar's%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20the%20hostages%20being%20released%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20office%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Israel%20had%20received%20an%20initial%20list%20of%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20from%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2050%20women%20and%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%2019%20being%20released%20by%20Hamas%20are%20three%20U.S.%20citizens%2C%20including%20a%20girl%20who%20turns%204%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20US%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Israeli%20civilians%20and%20soldiers%20taken%20on%20October%207%2C%20more%20than%20half%20the%20roughly%20240%20hostages%20are%20foreign%20and%20dual%20nationals%20from%20about%2040%20countries%20including%20Argentina%2C%20Britain%2C%20Chile%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Portugal%2C%20Spain%2C%20Thailand%20and%20the%20US%2C%20Israel's%20government%20has%20said.%20Not%20all%20the%20hostages%20taken%20on%20Oct.%207%20were%20being%20held%20by%20Hamas%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20the%20Palestinians%20being%20freed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20provided%20a%20list%20of%20about%20300%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20who%20might%20be%20released%20-%20double%20the%20number%20of%20women%20and%20minors%20it%20has%20agreed%20to%20be%20freed%20at%20first%20-%20and%20suggested%20it%20expects%20more%20than%2050%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20under%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Prisoners%20Society%20said%20that%20as%20of%20Wednesday%2C%207%2C200%20prisoners%20were%20being%20held%20by%20Israel%2C%20among%20them%2088%20women%20and%20250%20children%2017%20and%20under.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20on%20the%20list%20of%20300%20are%20from%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank%20and%20Jerusalem%20and%20were%20held%20for%20incidents%20such%20as%20attempted%20stabbings%2C%20hurling%20stones%20at%20Israeli%20soldiers%2C%20making%20explosives%2C%20damaging%20property%20and%20having%20contacts%20with%20hostile%20organisations.%20None%20are%20accused%20of%20murder.%20Many%20were%20held%20under%20administrative%20detention%2C%20meaning%20they%20were%20held%20without%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20released%20prisoners%20could%20be%20taken%20by%20buses%20to%20the%20presidential%20headquarters%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20first%20as%20in%20past%20releases%2C%20even%20though%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20had%20no%20role%20in%20these%20truce%20negotiations%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20negotiated%20the%20deal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatar%20played%20a%20major%20mediation%20role.%20Hamas%20has%20a%20political%20office%20in%20Doha%20and%20the%20Qatari%20government%20has%20kept%20channels%20of%20communication%20open%20with%20Israel%2C%20even%20though%20unlike%20some%20other%20Gulf%20Arab%20states%20it%20has%20not%20normalised%20ties%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20also%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%2C%20with%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20holding%20calls%20with%20Qatari%20Emir%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20bin%20Hamad%20Al%20Thani%20and%20Netanyahu%20in%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEgypt%2C%20the%20first%20Arab%20state%20to%20sign%20a%20peace%20deal%20with%20Israel%20and%20which%20has%20long%20played%20a%20mediation%20role%20over%20the%20decades%20of%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict%2C%20was%20also%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20has%20it%20taken%20so%20long%20to%20negotiate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20was%20announced%2046%20days%20after%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20fierce%20conflicts%20to%20erupt%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%20Hamas%20fighters%20killed%201%2C200%20people%20when%20they%20launched%20their%20raid%20on%20Israel%2C%20the%20biggest%20single-day%20toll%20on%20Israeli%20soil%20since%20its%20creation%20in%201948%2C%20and%20more%20than%2014%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20and%20land%20incursion%20since%20then%2C%20the%20most%20by%20far%20of%20any%20recent%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20such%20ferocious%20fighting%2C%20the%20large%20number%20of%20hostages%20and%20Israel's%20stated%20determination%20to%20wipe%20out%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%2C%20mediating%20even%20a%20temporary%20deal%2C%20like%20this%20one%2C%20proved%20far%20more%20challenging%20than%20in%20previous%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20negotiations%20for%20a%20deal%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20both%20sworn%20enemies%2C%20began%20within%20days%20of%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack%20but%20progress%20was%20slow.%20This%20was%20partly%20because%20communications%20between%20the%20warring%20sides%20had%20to%20go%20via%20Doha%20or%20Cairo%20and%20back%20for%20every%20detail%20hammered%20out%2C%20such%20as%20securing%20a%20full%20list%20from%20Hamas%20for%20those%20to%20be%20released%2C%20US%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20a%20deal%20in%20place%2C%20the%20ceasefire%20is%20temporary.%20Hamas%20has%20said%20throughout%20the%20truce%20its%20%26quot%3Bfingers%20remain%20on%20the%20trigger%26quot%3B.%20Israel%20has%20said%20the%20conflict%20will%20continue%20until%20all%20the%20hostages%20are%20freed%20and%20Hamas%20is%20eliminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20when%20Israel%20last%20launched%20a%20major%20land%20invasion%20in%20Gaza%2C%20it%20took%2049%20days%20for%20both%20sides%20to%20implement%20a%20ceasefire%20deal%2C%20but%20that%20brought%20major%20fighting%20to%20an%20end%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700809980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fd5tr28is_gaza-civilians-reuters_625x300_24_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2