2Frussia-says-downed-16-ukrainian-drones-in-south-crimea%2Famp_articleshow%2F105465832.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Credit%20Card%20Fraud%3A%20How%20To%20Stay%20Safe%2C%20What%20Do%20To%20If%20Card%20Details%20Stolen%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPaying%20for%20things%20digitally%20is%20so%20common%2C%20most%20of%20us%20think%20nothing%20of%20swiping%20or%20tapping%20our%20card%2C%20or%20using%20mobile%20payments.%20While%20doing%20so%20is%20second%20nature%2C%20we%20may%20be%20more%20reluctant%20to%20provide%20card%20details%20over%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerchants%20are%20allowed%20to%20ask%20us%20for%20credit%20card%20details%20over%20the%20phone%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20perfectly%20legal.%20But%20there%20are%20minimum%20standards%20they%20must%20comply%20with%20and%20safeguards%20to%20protect%20consumer%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20is%20giving%20your%20card%20details%20over%20the%20phone%20any%20more%20risky%20than%20other%20transactions%20and%20how%20can%20you%20minimise%20the%20risks%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20is%20my%20card%20data%20protected%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20merchant%20to%20process%20card%20transactions%2C%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs-prv.pcisecuritystandards.org%2FPCI%2520DSS%2FStandard%2FPCI-DSS-v4_0.pdf%5C%22%3EPayment%20Card%20Industry%20Data%20Security%20Standard%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20a%20set%20of%20security%20requirements%20designed%20to%20protect%20cardholder%20data%20and%20the%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20of%20transactions%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompliance%20involves%20various%20security%20measures%20(such%20as%20encryption%20and%20access%20controls)%20together%20with%20strong%20governance%20and%20regular%20security%20assessments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20information%20stored%20by%20the%20merchant%20is%20accessed%20by%20an%20unauthorised%20party%2C%20encryption%20ensures%20it%20is%20not%20readable.%20That%20means%20stealing%20the%20data%20would%20not%20let%20the%20criminals%20use%20the%20card%20details.%20Meanwhile%2C%20access%20controls%20ensure%20only%20authorised%20individuals%20have%20access%20to%20cardholder%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20all%20companies%20processing%20cards%20are%20expected%20to%20meet%20the%20compliance%20standards%2C%20only%20those%20processing%20large%20volumes%20are%20subject%20to%20mandatory%20regular%20audits.%20Should%20a%20subsequent%20data%20leak%20or%20misuse%20occur%20that%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20a%20compliance%20failure%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csoonline.com%2Farticle%2F569591%2Fpci-dss-explained-requirements-fines-and-steps-to-compliance.html%5C%22%3Ecompany%20can%20be%20penalised%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20levels%20that%20can%20escalate%20into%20millions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20requirements%20apply%20to%20all%20card%20transactions%2C%20whether%20in%20person%2C%20online%20or%20over%20the%20phone.%20Phone%20transactions%20are%20likely%20to%20involve%20a%20human%20collecting%20the%20card%20details%20and%20either%20entering%20them%20into%20computer%20systems%2C%20or%20processing%20the%20payment%20through%20paper%20forms.%20The%20payment%20card%20Security%20Standards%20Council%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs-prv.pcisecuritystandards.org%2FGuidance%2520Document%2FTelephone-Based%2520Payments%2FProtecting_Telephone_Based_Payment_Card_Data_v3-0_nov_2018.pdf%5C%22%3Edetailed%20guides%20for%20best%20practice%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20policy%20should%20be%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20that%20payment%20card%20data%20is%20protected%20against%20unauthorised%20viewing%2C%20copying%2C%20or%20scanning%2C%20in%20particular%20on%20desks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20these%20measures%20can%20help%20to%20protect%20your%20card%20data%2C%20there%20are%20still%20risks%20in%20case%20the%20details%20are%20misplaced%20or%20the%20person%20on%20the%20phone%20aren't%20who%20they%20say%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EBasic%20tips%20for%20safe%20credit%20card%20use%20over%20the%20phone%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20provide%20card%20details%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20there%20are%20steps%20you%20can%20take%20to%20minimise%20the%20chance%20you'll%20become%20the%20victim%20of%20fraud%2C%20or%20get%20your%20details%20leaked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Verify%20the%20caller%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20didn't%20initiate%20the%20call%2C%20hang%20up%20and%20call%20the%20company%20directly%20using%20details%20you've%20verified%20yourself.%20Scammers%20will%20often%20masquerade%20as%20a%20well-known%20company%20(for%20example%2C%20an%20online%20retailer%20or%20a%20courier)%20and%20convince%20you%20a%20payment%20failed%20or%20payment%20is%20needed%20to%20release%20a%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20provide%20any%20information%2C%20confirm%20the%20caller%20is%20legitimate%20and%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20call%20is%20genuine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Be%20sceptical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20being%20offered%20a%20deal%20that's%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%2C%20have%20concerns%20about%20the%20person%20you're%20dealing%20with%2C%20or%20just%20feel%20something%20is%20not%20quite%20right%2C%20hang%20up.%20You%20can%20always%20call%20them%20back%20later%20if%20the%20caller%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20legitimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Use%20secure%20payment%20methods%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20previously%20paid%20the%20company%20with%20other%20(more%20secure)%20methods%2C%20ask%20to%20use%20that%20same%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Keep%20records%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20sure%20you%20record%20details%20of%20the%20company%2C%20the%20representative%20you%20are%20speaking%20to%20and%20the%20amount%20being%20charged.%20You%20should%20also%20ask%20for%20an%20order%20or%20transaction%20reference.%20Don't%20forget%20to%20ask%20for%20the%20receipt%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECheck%20the%20transaction%20against%20your%20card%20matches%20the%20receipt%20%E2%80%93%20use%20your%20banking%20app%2C%20don't%20wait%20for%20the%20statement%20to%20come%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F560960%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20231122-15-8f2rll.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26q%3D45%26auto%3Dformat%26w%3D1000%26fit%3Dclip%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Close%20up%20of%20a%20hand%20entering%20pin%20code%20at%20an%20ATM%5C%22%20sizes%3D%5C%22(min-width%3A%201466px)%20754px%2C%20(max-width%3A%20599px)%20100vw%2C%20(min-width%3A%20600px)%20600px%2C%20237px%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F560960%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20231122-15-8f2rll.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D45%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D600%26amp%3Bh%3D400%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D1%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F560960%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20231122-15-8f2rll.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D30%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D600%26amp%3Bh%3D400%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D2%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F560960%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20231122-15-8f2rll.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D15%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D600%26amp%3Bh%3D400%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D3%201800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F560960%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20231122-15-8f2rll.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D45%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D754%26amp%3Bh%3D503%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D1%20754w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F560960%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20231122-15-8f2rll.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D30%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D754%26amp%3Bh%3D503%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D2%201508w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F560960%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20231122