20Shehla%20(no%20longer%20my%20comrade)%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20you%20are%20doing%20well%20and%20are%20in%20a%20very%20good%20place%20now.%20Watching%20your%20podcast%20was%20difficult%20for%20me.%20However%2C%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20say%20I%20am%20sad%2C%20angry%2C%20or%20upset.%20I%20would%20say%20I%20am%20a%20little%20disappointed.%20You%20spoke%20about%20the%20selfless%20service%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20which%20has%20caused%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20in%20you.%20Well%2C%20hearts%20do%20keep%20changing%20and%20breaking%2C%20but%20heartlessness%20is%20systemic%20and%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20left%20the%20student%20movement%2C%20especially%20left%20organisations%2C%20for%20various%20reasons%2C%20including%20furthering%20their%20own%20interests%20in%20other%20parties.%20However%2C%20most%20largely%20remained%20within%20the%20anti-fascist%20front%20or%20parties%20fighting%20it.%20You%20too%2C%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20have%20disassociated%20yourself%20from%20the%20left%20movement%20and%20the%20student%20movement%20you%20represented.%20I%2C%20along%20with%20others%2C%20despite%20being%20disappointed%2C%20respected%20your%20decision.%20However%2C%20my%20disappointment%20now%20lies%20in%20your%20ever-changing%20positions.%20You%20are%20entitled%20to%20your%20views%2C%20opinions%2C%20and%20constant%20changes%20of%20heart.%20However%2C%20what%20bothers%20me%20is%20the%20heartlessness.%20I%20am%20saying%20this%20not%20from%20the%20position%20of%20being%20a%20former%20JNU%20student%20union%20president%20or%20as%20a%20student%20activist%20whom%20you%20sat%20with%20for%20long%20hours%20debating%2C%20nor%20as%20a%20friend%20who%20has%20several%20pleasant%20memories%20of%20working%20with%20you.%20I%20am%20saying%20this%20from%20a%20moral%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20political%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20your%20interview%20to%20ANI%2C%20you%20claimed%20that%20you%20had%20this%20sudden%20change%20of%20heart%20after%20seeing%20the%20great%20service%20of%20Modi%20and%20Shah.%20But%20strangely%2C%20you%20conveniently%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20series%20of%20changes%20of%20heart%20you%20have%20had%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20I%20think%20you%20should%20also%20enlighten%20why%20you%20floated%20a%20party%20only%20to%20dissolve%20it%20later%2C%20and%20why%20you%20decided%20to%20file%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20only%20to%20have%20another%20change%20of%20heart%20and%20withdraw%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yes%2C%20I%20feel%20disappointed.%20Let%20me%20explain%20why%20I%20feel%20this%20way.%20My%20friend%20Umar%20Khalid%20is%20languishing%20in%20jail.%20Similarly%2C%20many%20Kashmiri%20journalists%2C%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20and%20other%20innocent%20people%20are%20in%20jails%20without%20any%20trial%20and%20under%20trumped%20up%20charges%20of%20UAPA.%20Father%20Stan%20Swamy%20passed%20away%20in%20jail%20facing%20a%20false%20and%20politically%20motivated%20case%20in%20the%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20matter%20and%20was%20not%20even%20provided%20with%20a%20straw%20to%20eat%20food.%20Fatima%20Nafees%20is%20still%20fighting%20to%20find%20her%20son.%20Radhika%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eamma%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20still%20battling%20all%20odds%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20Rohith%20Vemula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20surprises%20me%20is%20that%20you%20were%20part%20of%20all%20these%20movements.%20Not%20only%20these%20but%20many%20more.%20It%20is%20this%20heartlessness%20where%20I%20wish%20to%20draw%20a%20line.%20The%20way%20you%20whitewashed%20the%20crimes%20of%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20by%20praising%20them%20for%20being%20%E2%80%9Cselfless%E2%80%9D%20cannot%20just%20be%20a%20change%20of%20heart.%20For%20their%20histories%20to%20be%20forgiven%20and%20forgotten%2C%20for%20which%20there%20has%20never%20been%20remorse%2C%20requires%20not%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20but%20maybe%20an%20absence%20of%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20who%20faced%20witch%20hunts%2C%20unable%20to%20fight%20for%20whatever%20reasons%2C%20either%20became%20silent%2C%20left%20the%20country%20or%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20political%20path.%20Yet%2C%20they%20did%20not%20turn%20into%20supporters%20of%20what%20is%20a%20palpably%20fascist%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20podcast%2C%20you%20spoke%20about%20a%20flirtation%20with%20revolutionary%20politics%20in%20your%2020s.%20Well%2C%20what%20made%20journalist%20Smita%20Prakash%20sit%20with%20you%20and%20give%20value%20to%20your%20opinions%20is%20this%20very%20flirtation%20with%20revolutionary%20politics%20and%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20hundreds%20and%20thousands%20of%20students%20on%20which%20it%20is%20founded.%20Remember%20that%20Bhagat%20Singh%20was%20in%20his%2020s%20when%20he%20was%20martyred%20fighting%20for%20the%20nation.%20There%20are%20hundreds%20of%20such%20examples%20in%20our%20freedom%20movement%2C%20post-independence%2C%20and%20from%20the%20campus%20you%20graduated.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20story%20of%20Chandrashekar%20Prasad%2C%20twice-elected%20JNUSU%20President%20who%20was%20killed%20by%20feudal%20goons%20for%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20landless%20people.%20By%20the%20way%2C%20he%20was%20in%20his%2020s%20too.%20It%20is%20the%20cynical%20and%20corrupted%20who%20find%20the%20revolutionary%20zeal%20of%20those%20in%20their%2020s%20mere%20%E2%80%98idealistic%E2%80%99.%20To%20dismiss%20the%20honesty%20of%20this%20spirit%2C%20as%20you%20have%20done%2C%20is%20to%20demean%20and%20insult%20the%20struggles%20and%20movements%20of%20students%20in%20universities%2C%20the%20very%20movements%20that%20have%20contributed%20to%20your%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20term%20your%20interactions%20and%20time%20with%20many%20of%20us%20as%20%E2%80%98being%20in%20an%20echo%20chamber%E2%80%99%20only%20made%20me%20question%20my%20own%20earlier%20appreciation%20of%20your%20intelligence%2C%20political%20acumen%2C%20and%20nuanced%20articulations.%20Again%2C%20let%20me%20remind%20you%2C%20that%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98echo%20chamber%E2%80%99%20helped%20you%20shape%20your%20opinions%20and%20positions%20which%20the%20people%20resisting%20fascism%20welcomed%20with%20open%20hearts.%20Now%20to%20turn%20around%20and%20be%20dismissive%20only%20shows%20you%20are%20capable%20of%20disowning%20anything%2C%20if%20need%20be.%20What%20guarantee%20is%20it%20that%20once%20the%20current%20regime%20is%20defeated%2C%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20again%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20this%20zeal%20is%20not%20restricted%20to%20the%2020s.%20May%20I%20remind%20you%20that%20Father%20Stan%20Swamy%20was%20not%20in%20his%2020s%2C%20nor%20are%20Fatima%20Nafees%20(Najeeb%E2%80%99s%20mother)%2C%20Radhika%20Amma%20(Rohith%E2%80%99s%20Mother)%2C%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20(%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0editor)%2C%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%2C%20and%20many%20others%20who%20are%20fighting%20for%20justice%20and%20are%20hounded%20for%20exposing%20crony%20capitalism%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlease%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20face%20the%20reality%20that%20your%20past%20association%20with%20left%20and%20progressive%20movements%20may%20be%20coming%20in%20the%20way%20of%20your%20future%20aspirations%2C%20and%20that%20you%20need%20to%20part%20ways%20%E2%80%93%20which%20you%20actually%20did%20a%20long%20time%20ago.%20We%20understood%20and%20never%20pointed%20fingers.%20However%2C%20if%20your%20compulsions%20or%20aspirations%20require%20insulting%20those%20very%20movements%2C%20then%20difficult%20questions%20will%20be%20asked%20about%20your%20change%20of%20heart.%20Is%20it%20really%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20or%20a%20change%20of%20direction%20in%20which%20the%20heart%20wishes%20to%20see%20some%20things%20and%20also%20%E2%80%98unsee%E2%80%99%20much%20more%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20these%20twisted%20ethical%20and%20political%20positions%20that%20are%20enabling%20fundamentalists%20to%20destroy%20India%20that%20I%20find%20difficult%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with.%20Many%20people%20have%20written%20and%20are%20saying%20that%20there%20must%20be%20some%20compulsions%20and%20pressures%20on%20you%20to%20take%20this%20drastic%20step.%20Well%2C%20if%20a%20common%20citizen%2C%20who%20is%20just%20going%20about%20their%20life%20who%20is%20facing%20the%20music%20of%20unemployment%2C%20harassment%2C%20price%20rise%2C%20and%20others%20is%20still%20resisting%2C%20voting%2C%20and%20fighting%20to%20keep%20BJP%20away%2C%20a%20lot%20is%20expected%20from%20people%20like%20us%20who%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20student%20and%20anti-fascist%20movements%20and%20have%20benefited%20from%20critical%20scholarship.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20you%20gave%20up%20and%20decided%20to%20turn%20sides.%20It%20is%20disheartening%20but%20not%20demotivating%2C%20as%20there%20are%20millions%20still%20resisting%20the%20BJP%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20present%20times%2C%20as%20a%20young%20research%20scholar%2C%20one%20just%20has%20to%20go%20to%20a%20job%20interview%20at%20Delhi%20University%20to%20see%20the%20consequences%20of%20commitment%20to%20a%20secular%2C%20socialist%2C%20democratic%2C%20and%20egalitarian%20nation.%20People%20are%20risking%20their%20careers%2C%20taking%20positions%20they%20are%20over-qualified%20for%20just%20because%20they%20opposed%20the%20ABVP.%20Yet%2C%20they%20are%20standing%20strong%20and%20refusing%20to%20give%20in%20to%20get%20a%20job.%20These%20are%20inspiring%20people%20to%20me%3B%20I%20find%20motivation%20to%20strive%20more%20and%20be%20upright%20in%20what%20we%20do%20in%20life.%20I%20find%20inspiration%20in%20people%20who%20refuse%20to%20strike%20bargains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20am%20not%20in%20my%2020s%20anymore%2C%20so%20please%20ignore%20my%20opinion%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EN.%20Sai%20Balaji%20is%20a%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%