cious%20hate%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20orchestrated%20by%20Hindutva%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanditaradhya%20Shivacharya%20Swami%20of%20the%20Sanehalli%20matha%20in%20Chitradurga%20district%20of%20Karnataka%20had%20asked%20Lingayats%20to%20stop%20worshipping%20Ganapati%20three%20weeks%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CGanapati%20is%20not%20Lingayat%20culture.%20Instead%20of%20starting%20events%20with%20a%20prayer%20to%20him%2C%20Lingayats%20should%20sing%20Vachanas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%20Lingayats%20consider%20Vachanas%2C%20short%20prose-poems%20composed%20by%20Sharanas%20or%20their%20founding%20fathers%2C%20as%20their%20holy%20scripture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20swami%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20triggered%20a%20massive%20backlash%20from%20Hindutva%20groups%2C%20prompting%20his%20supporters%20to%20organise%20a%20meeting%20at%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20Gandhi%20Bhavan%20and%20chalk%20out%20a%20plan%20to%20counter%20the%20campaign%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20noted%20that%20the%20vilification%20campaign%20against%20the%20swami%20was%20following%20a%20trajectory%20that%20had%20earlier%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20Professor%20M.M.%20Kalburgi%20and%20journalist%20Gauri%20Lankesh.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20begins%20as%20a%20verbal%20attack%20ends%20in%20physical%20assault%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20writer%20Banjagere%20Jayaprakasha%2C%20who%20with%20a%20few%20other%20activists%2C%20S.%20G.%20Siddaramiah%2C%20Mavalli%20Shankar%20and%20Siddana%20Gowda%20Patil%2C%20briefed%20the%20media%20later.%20The%20names%20of%20the%20other%20participants%20have%20been%20withheld%20as%20the%20main%20event%20was%20held%20behind%20closed%20doors%20to%20allow%20a%20free%20flow%20of%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20event%2C%20an%20editor%20of%20a%20rapidly%20emerging%20Kannada%20news%20website%20said%20the%20police%20charge%20sheet%20on%20Kalburgi%E2%80%99s%20murder%20mentions%20Kannada%20TV%20channels%2C%20which%20ran%20a%20relentless%20campaign%20against%20him%20whipping%20up%20hatred.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20found%20that%20an%20edited%20video%20clip%20of%20a%20Gauri%20speech%20had%20been%20shown%20to%20her%20alleged%20killer%20again%20and%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CA%20man%20who%20was%20recently%20arrested%20from%20Davanagere%20for%20writing%20threat%20letters%20to%20several%20writers%20has%20links%20with%20the%20alleged%20killers%20of%20Kalburgi%20and%20Gauri%2C%20according%20to%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20speakers%20said%20there%20was%20an%20organised%20attempt%20to%20intimidate%20activists%2C%20who%20dissented%20from%20the%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20religion%2C%20one%20language%20narrative.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20went%20after%20Panditaradhya%20Swamiji%2C%20ridiculing%20and%20abusing%20him%20with%20savage%20words%20without%20caring%20for%20his%20revered%20position%20in%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20participant.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20back%20off.%20We%20have%20to%20push%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20book%20translated%20by%20a%20writer%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20a%20Bangalore%20university%20professor%20noted%20that%20political%20violence%20was%20endemic%20in%20ancient%20India%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20intolerance%20we%20are%20witnessing%20now%20is%20historically%20unprecedented.%20Our%20inertia%20is%20their%20asset%2C%20we%20need%20to%20unite%20and%20counter%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20professor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoted%20Dalit%20rights%20leader%20Mavallli%20Shankar%20recalled%20that%20Dalits%20in%20Maharashtra%20had%20mobilised%20massively%20when%20the%20Hindutva%20groups%20had%20tried%20to%20censor%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ERiddles%20of%20Hinduism%3C%2Fem%3E%20book%20in%20the%201980s.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20show%20a%20similar%20strength%20in%20Karnataka%20now.%20The%20swamiji%2C%20who%20speaks%20for%20Basava%2C%20has%20to%20lead%20this%20effort%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20speakers%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20progressive%20response%20had%20to%20go%20beyond%20reacting%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20provocation%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20constructive%20agenda%20instead.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20a%20100-year%20plan%20and%20all%20we%20have%20is%20knee%20jerk%20reactions%20to%20counter%20it.%20We%20need%20to%20build%20an%20alternate%20model%20of%20cultural%20politics%20and%20take%20it%20to%20people%20in%20all%20the%206%2C000%20panchayats%20of%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20leading%20experts%20on%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20him%20a%20noted%20writer%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20radicalising%20our%20brothers%20from%20backward%20communities%20to%20attack%20us.%20We%20need%20to%20hold%20camps%20for%20our%20youth%20and%20prepare%20a%20few%20thousand%20cadres.%E2%80%9D%20He%20noted%20that%20Dalit%20youths%20in%20Karnataka%20were%20politically%20aware%20thanks%20to%20Professor%20B.%20Krishnappa%2C%20who%20began%20organising%20training%20camps%20in%20the%201980s.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20time%20for%20other%20communities%20such%20as%20Lingayats%2C%20Vokkaligas%20and%20Kurubas%20to%20follow%20that%20model%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Krishnappa%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20Dalit%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%2C%20led%20many%20landmark%20struggles%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20everyone%20who%20spoke%20at%20the%20event%20urged%20Panditaradhya%20swami%20to%20revive%20his%20popular%20mass%20contact%20programme%20%E2%80%98Matthe%20Kalyana%E2%80%99%20or%20Kalyana%20Again.%20The%2012th-century%20city%20of%20Kalyana%20was%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Lingayat%20movement%20that%20sought%20to%20create%20a%20society%20of%20equals.%20The%20swami%20had%20launched%20%E2%80%98Matthe%20Kalyana%E2%80%99%20in%202019%20in%20all%2030%20districts%20of%20the%20state%20to%20rekindle%20the%20progressive%20spirit%20of%20Kalyana%20through%20plays%20and%20lectures.%20He%20had%20travelled%20extensively%2C%20engaging%20hundreds%20of%20students%20and%20local%20residents%20in%20freewheeling%20discussions%20where%20anyone%20could%20ask%20him%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20lunch%2C%20a%20farmer%20activist%20said%20Hindutva%20groups%20had%20picked%20on%20the%20wrong%20swami.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20been%20attacked%20before%2C%20he%20knows%20how%20to%20handle%20it.%20He%20is%20deeply%20ideological%20and%20a%20smart%20organiser%2C%20who%20can%20mobilise%20people%20and%20funds%20anywhere%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20controversy%20has%20now%20turned%20him%20into%20a%20huge%20icon%20for%20progressive%20and%20Lingayat%20groups%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lingayat%20branding%20of%20the%20new%20initiative%20to%20counter%20Hindutva%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20tricky.%20The%20Hindutva%20campaign%20against%20the%20swami%20drew%20immediate%20response%20from%20Lingayat%20activists%2C%20who%20are%20fighting%20for%20a%20separate%20religion.%20They%20interpreted%20the%20attack%20on%20him%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98attack%20on%20Basava%20philosophy%E2%80%99%20as%20both%20had%20spoken%20up%20against%20superstition.%20The%20event%20was%20also%20held%20under%20the%20banner%2C%20Pragnavantara%20Anubhava%20Mantapa%2C%20named%20after%20a%2012th%20century%20forum%20in%20which%20sharanas%20took%20part%20in%20wide%20ranging%20discussions%20without%20any%20caste%20or%20gender%20barrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20participants%20like%20Professor%20S.G.%20Siddaramiah%20saw%20the%20new%20initiative%20as%20a%20continuation%20of%20the%20medieval%20movement%20led%20by%20reformer%20Basavanna%2C%20which%20had%20strongly%20come%20out%20strongly%20against%20a%20hierarchical%20and%20exclusive%20sanatana%20dharma.%20But%20one%20participant%20dissented%20and%20said%20Buddha%2C%20Basava%20and%20Ambedkar%20should%20be%20explicitly%20mentioned%20to%20make%20the%20effort%20more%20broad%20based.%20A%20prominent%20Dalit%20activist%20cautioned%20against%20letting%20narrow%20identities%20seep%20in%20and%20said%20to%20be%20successful%20the%20campaign%20would%20have%20to%20transcend%20caste.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%20the%20Dalit%20movement%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20progressive%20act%20to%20bring%20together%20the%20most%20deprived%20castes.%20But%20the%20caste%20identity%20proved%20to%20be%20counterproductive%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20Basavanna%E2%80%99s%20ideals%20were%20inspiring%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20find%20Lingayats%2C%20who%20lived%20by%20them%2C%20triggering%20an%20uproar%20from%20many%20participants%2C%20with%20one%20of%20them%20angrily%20asking%20him%20not%20to%20generalise.%20The%20main%20organiser%20of%20the%20event%2C%20Siddappa%20Mulge%2C%20said%20the%20initiative%20was%20a%20response%20of%20progressive%20groups%2C%20not%20just%20Lingayats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20also%20think%20that%20the%20Lingayat%20participation%20and%20Panditaradhya%20Swami%E2%80%98s%20leadership%20may%20help%20in%20mobilising%20the%20large%20community%2C%20which%20forms%20the%20main%20vote%20bank%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20Karnataka.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20these%20meetings%20we%20usually%20see%20the%20same%20people%20sitting%20across%20the%20table.%20It%20is%20refreshing%20to%20see%20so%20many%20new%20faces%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Siddana%20Gowda%20Patil%2C%20possibly%20commenting%20on%20the%20heavy%20Lingayat%20presence%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanditaradhya%20Swami%2C%20who%20presided%20over%20the%20meeting%2C%20said%20the%20initiative%20would%20follow%20the%20ideals%20of%20Buddha%2C%20Basava%2C%20Ambedkar%20and%20Gandhi%2C%20among%20others.%20Agreeing%20that%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20people%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20be%20bringing%20out%2010%20small%20books%20within%20a%20month%20and%20asked%20the%20writers%20at%20the%20venue%20to%20send%20proposals%20for%20short%20books%2C%20which%20would%20encourage%20rational%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20open%20to%20reviving%20the%20Matthe%20Kalyana%20campaign%20and%20asked%20the%20participants%20to%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20of%2015%20people%20with%20members%20from%20all%20communities.%20He%20noted%20that%20the%20previous%20edition%20of%20Matthe%20Kalyana%20did%20not%20have%20just%20Lingayats%20and%20it%20was%20the%20Dalit%20groups%2C%20which%20had%20made%20it%20successful.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Ballari%20Muslims%20had%20organised%20the%20event%20and%20the%20food.%20The%20event%20In%20Mangaluru%20started%20with%20a%20prayer%20from%20a%20Muslim%20girl%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20willing%20to%20change%20and%20become%20more%20aware.%20We%20just%20have%20to%20take%20them%20on%20the%20right%20path%2C%E2%80%9C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.A.%20Arun%20is%20a%20Bangalore-based%20writer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700753686000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23210350%2FIMG-20231123-WA0233.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flingayat-swamis-supporters-plan-antidote-to-hate-campaign%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20speakers%20at%20a%20Bengaluru%20event%20said%20there%20was%20an%20organised%20attempt%20to%20intimidate%20activists%2C%20who%20dissented%20from%20the%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20religion%2C%20one%20language%20narrative.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flingayat-swamis-supporters-plan-antidote-to-hate-campaign%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20migrants%20found%20dead%20in%20Channel%20after%20trying%20to%20reach%20UK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700751660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-boulogne-sur-mer-france_6369611.jpg%3F20231123143229%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.