hment%20crisis%20with%2016%25%20of%20its%20population%20malnourished%20compared%20to%20the%20global%20average%20of%208%25.%20This%20three-part%20investigation%20traces%20the%20structural%20causes%20of%20hunger%20and%20food%20insecurity%20in%20inequalities%20in%20power%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20policy%20of%20rice%20fortification%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20public-sector%20food%20programmes.%20It%20examines%20the%20solutions%20the%20state%20is%20offering%20to%20ask%20what%20their%20true%20meaning%20is%20for%20people%20and%20the%20climate.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20mandatory%20rice%20fortification%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20public-sector%20food%20programmes%2C%20identifies%20the%20gaps%20in%20quality%20control.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3EState%20governments%20were%20given%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20switch%20to%20distributing%20chemically-fortified%20rice%2C%20even%20where%20infrastructure%20for%20quality%20was%20absent%2C%20or%20far%20from%20assured.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EIn%20villages%2C%20even%20those%20who%20question%20the%20policy%20are%20told%20to%20eat%20the%20new%20rice%2C%20artificially%20fortified%20with%20factory-made%20micronutrients.%20Adivasi%20farmers%20who%20have%20the%20knowledge%20and%20practice%20of%20growing%20a%20variety%20of%20rice%2C%20pulses%2C%20millets%2C%20and%20gathering%20tubers%2C%20small%20game%2C%20mushrooms%2C%20berries%20from%20the%20forest%20are%20further%20pushed%20to%20cereal-heavy%20diets%2C%20that%20have%20over%20time%20depleted%20soils%20and%20worsened%20nutrition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERead%20part%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fplastic-rice-why-union-govts-experiment-with-an-artificial-grain-is-hard-to-swallow-for-rural-adivasis%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERanchi%2FLatehar%20(Jharkhand)%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20reduce%20anaemi