20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20these%20cases%20were%20being%20heard%2C%20the%20project%20rolled%20on.%20In%20February%202018%2C%20the%20Cabinet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1521024%5C%22%3Eapproved%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Barkot-Silkyara%20tunnel%20%E2%80%93%20between%20Gangotri%20and%20Yamunotri.%20In%20June%202018%2C%20the%20state-owned%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20(NHIDCL)%20awarded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F11%2F20%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-highlights-himalayan-fragility-and-the-need-for-escape-routes%5C%22%3Ethe%20tender%20for%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F11%2F20%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-highlights-himalayan-fragility-and-the-need-for-escape-routes%5C%22%3Etunnel%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Hyderabad-based%20Navayuga%20Engineering%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20year%2C%20Navayuga%20hired%20a%20German-Austrian%20engineering%20consultancy%20called%20Bernard%20Gruppe%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bernard-gruppe.com%2Fen%2F2023%2F08%2F09%2Fsilkyara-tunnel%2F%5C%22%3Edesign%20and%20build%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20Sikkim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20before%20Silkyara%2C%20geological%20risks%20had%20hammered%20another%20infrastructure%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sikkim%2C%20a%20glacial%20lake%20burst%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20Teesta%20punching%20its%20way%20through%201%2C200%20megawatt%20Teesta%20III%20in%20the%20upper%20reaches%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13172524%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-5.24.22%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13172524%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-5.24.22%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13172524%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-5.24.22%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x166.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679982%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22566%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20devastated%E2%80%9D%20dam%20site%20area%20of%20Teesta-III.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%20%40shubhamtorres09%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Teesta%20III%20and%20Silkyara%20are%20analogous%20tales.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20the%20dam%2C%20locals%E2%80%99%20warnings%20about%20glacial%20lakes%20had%20been%20ignored.%20As%20a%20forthcoming%20story%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20show%2C%20its%20construction%20was%20handed%20out%20to%20an%20untested%20firm%20which%20was%20just%20four%20months%20old%20when%20it%20bagged%20the%20tender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20Sikkim%20and%20the%20dam%20management%20failed%20to%20enshrine%20disaster%20management%20and%20dam%20safety%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20what%20happened%20thereafter.%20Geological%20risks%20%E2%80%93%20ignored%20during%20the%20environmental%20clearance%20process%20%E2%80%93%20asserted%20themselves%20once%20construction%20started.%20The%20dam%20site%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20landslide%20and%20then%20by%20an%20earthquake.%20Both%20resulted%20in%20construction%20delays%2C%20and%20left%20the%20hydel%20project%20unviable.%20Then%20came%20the%20glacial%20flood%2C%20and%20took%20the%20dam%20out%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnel%20at%20Silkyara%20has%20traced%20a%20similar%20trajectory.%20Once%20construction%20began%2C%20Navayuga%20ran%20into%20geological%20surprises.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20start%20of%20tunnel%20driving%2C%20the%20geological%20conditions%20have%20proved%20to%20be%20more%20challenging%20than%20predicted%20in%20the%20tender%20documents%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bernard%20Gruppe%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bernard-gruppe.com%2Fen%2F2023%2F08%2F09%2Fsilkyara-tunnel%2F%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20Navayuga%20took%20a%20series%20of%20decisions%20which%20amplified%20workers%E2%80%99%20vulnerability%20to%20geological%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20glaring%20of%20these%20decisions%20was%20the%20failure%20to%20build%20an%20escape%20passage%2C%20as%20stipulated%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1521024%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20cabinet%20approval%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20if%20the%20company%20wanted%20to%20build%20such%20a%20passage%20%E2%80%93%20for%20travellers%20%E2%80%93%20only%20after%20completing%20the%20main%20tunnel%2C%20it%20needed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frapiduplift%2Fstatus%2F1726440504173453735%5C%22%3Ebuild%20an%20escape%20route%20for%20workers%20in%20the%20case%20of%20an%20emergency%20during%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESo%20many%20red%20flags%20in%20the%20Uttarkashi%20tunnel%20construction%20project.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHVrLjDu0E7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHVrLjDu0E7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Suvrat%20Kher%20(%40rapiduplift)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frapiduplift%2Fstatus%2F1726440504173453735%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20omission%20went%20unchallenged%20by%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%3B%20by%20NHIDCL%3B%20and%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways.%20It%20stayed%20unchallenged%20even%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fsamruddhi-expressway-accident-sub-contractors-booked-crane-collapse-kills-8871230%2F%5C%22%3Ean%20accident%20at%20another%20Navayuga%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fsamruddhi-expressway-accident-sub-contractors-booked-crane-collapse-kills-8871230%2F%5C%22%3Eproject%20site%20this%20August%3C%2Fa%3E%20claimed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fconstruction-workers-dead-in-thane-after-girder-falls-on-samruddhi-expressway%2Farticle67144813.ece%5C%22%3E20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fconstruction-workers-dead-in-thane-after-girder-falls-on-samruddhi-expressway%2Farticle67144813.ece%5C%22%3E%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20resulted%20in%20a%20case%20of%20negligence%20being%20filed%20against%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20what%20happened%20next.%20A%20part%20of%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20collapsed%2C%20maybe%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F11%2F20%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-highlights-himalayan-fragility-and-the-need-for-escape-routes%5C%22%3Eexplosives%20were%20used%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20maybe%20because%20the%20mountain%20itself%20was%20fragile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hours%20and%20days%20after%20the%20collapse%2C%20further%20evidence%20of%20Navayuga%E2%80%99s%20unpreparedness%20came%20to%20light.%20Rescue%20equipment%20like%20drilling%20machines%20were%20not%20available%20at%20hand.%20They%20had%20to%20be%20flown%20in.%20Even%20as%20the%20government%20began%20pushing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-collapse-multivitamins-anti-depressants-sent-to-trapped-workers-2464912-2023-11-19%5C%22%3Evitamins%20and%20anti-depressants%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers%20through%20a%20four-inch%20pipe%2C%20their%20diet%20stayed%20suboptimal%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fbleak-tunnel-vision-trapped-workers-stare-at-health-crisis%2Farticleshow%2F105320669.cms%5C%22%3Ed%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fbleak-tunnel-vision-trapped-workers-stare-at-health-crisis%2Farticleshow%2F105320669.cms%5C%22%3Ery%20fruits%2C%20puffed%20rice%20and%20popcorn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20after%20nine%20days%2C%20when%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkhichdi-in-bottles-1st-hot-meal-for-trapped-uttarakhand-tunnel-workers-in-9-days-4590699%5C%22%3Esix-inch%20pipe%20was%20eventually%20pushed%20through%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20workers%2C%20did%20they%20get%20their%20first%20cooked%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20preparation%20drew%20flak%20from%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20commencing%20work%20on%20such%20projects%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20have%20safety%20protocols%20in%20place%20and%20also%20have%20rescue%20plans%20in%20case%20of%20emergencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fhemant-soren-slams-central-government-over-tunnel-mishap-in-uttarkashi%2Fcid%2F1981922%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20situation%20is%20that%20even%20after%20so%20many%20days%2C%20there%20are%20talks%20of%20hiring%20foreign%20experts%20for%20rescue%20works.%20We%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20wait.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20asked%20Navayuga%20why%20the%20escape%20tunnel%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20built%2C%20if%20it%20had%20used%20explosives%2C%20and%20why%20it%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20planned%20for%20contingencies%20despite%20multiple%20warnings%20about%20the%20Himalayas%20being%20fragile%20and%20unstable.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20it%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20questions%2C%20however%2C%20scratch%20the%20surface.%20Silkyara%20(and%20Teesta%20III)%20are%20proverbial%20canaries%20in%20a%20mine%2C%20giving%20us%20a%20deeper%20warning%20than%20just%20the%20specific%20infirmities%20of%20these%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-sikkim-cm-cannot-evade-responsibility-on-the-teesta-dam-breach%5C%22%3EThe%20Sikkim%20CM%20Cannot%20Evade%20Responsibility%20on%20the%20Teesta%20Dam%20Breach%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ceded%20landscape%20of%20environmental%20protections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20May%206%2C%202020%2C%20history%20repeated%20itself%20in%20Vizag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%203%20am%20that%20night%2C%20a%20neuro-toxic%20gas%20leaked%20from%20a%20chemical%20plant%20of%20LG%20Polymers%20and%20spread%20into%20the%20colonies%20abutting%20the%20plant.%20Thirty-six%20years%20after%20the%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy%2C%20Indians%20again%20woke%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fvizag-factory-chemical-gas-leak-victim-account-recounts-horror-breathlessness-burning-eyes%5C%22%3Estruggling%20to%20breath%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fvizag-factory-chemical-gas-leak-victim-account-recounts-horror-breathlessness-burning-eyes%5C%22%3Ee%2C%20their%20eyes%20b%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fvizag-factory-chemical-gas-leak-victim-account-recounts-horror-breathlessness-burning-eyes%5C%22%3Eurning%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20least%2011%20people%20died%20in%20the%20incident.%20About%205%2C000%20were%20hospitalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20that%20followed%2C%20it%20emerged%20that%20the%20plant%20had%20been%20running%20without%20an%20environmental%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20sobering%20moment.%20After%20the%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy%2C%20India%20passed%20new%20laws%2C%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flegislative.gov.in%2Factsofparliamentfromtheyear%2Fenvironment-protection-act-1986%5C%22%3EEnvironment%20Protection%20Act%20(EPA)%2C%201986%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flegislative.gov.in%2Factsofparliamentfromtheyear%2Fpublic-liability-insurance-act-1991%5C%22%3EPublic%20Liability%20Insurance%20Act%20(PLIA)%2C%201991%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20amended%20existing%20ones%2C%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flegislative.gov.in%2Factsofparliamentfromtheyear%2Ffactories-act-1948%5C%22%3EFactories%20Act%2C%201948%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20public%20costs%20of%20industries%20working%20with%20hazardous%20technologies%20and%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20these%20laws%20too%20were%20weakened%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20night%20in%20Vizag%2C%20the%20full%20scale%20of%20usurped%20environmental%20protections%20became%20suddenly%20visible.%20As%20%3Cem%3EArticle-14%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.article-14.com%2Fpost%2Findia-is-back-to-a-time-before-the-bhopal-gas-tragedy%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20poisonous%20gas%20leaks%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fgross-negligence-lack-of-training-caused-vizag-gas-leak-report-1683735-2020-05-30%5C%22%3Epoorly%20maintained%3C%2Fa%3E%20industrial%20unit%2C%20operating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mongabay.com%2F2020%2F05%2Fyears-of-neglect-led-to-vizag-gas-tragedy%2F%5C%22%3Ewithout%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20environmental%20clearance%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20residential%20neighbourhoods%2C%20it%20invites%20more%20than%20comparisons%20with%20Union%20Carbide.%20It%20forces%20the%20belated%20recognition%20that%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20effective%20protection%20against%20industrial%20pollution%2C%20India%20is%20back%20where%20she%20was%20before%20the%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%