y%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.article-14.com%2Fpost%2Findia-is-back-to-a-time-before-the-bhopal-gas-tragedy%5C%22%3Eweakened%20its%20environmental%20governance%20architecture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20cynical%20game.%20For%20over%2020%20years%2C%20the%20environment%20ministry%20has%20been%20presented%20as%20a%20roadblock%2C%20delaying%20the%20construction%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20industrial%20plants%20and%20infrastructure%20projects.%20The%20ministry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fcompany%2Fcorporate-trends%2Findia-inc-unhappy-over-delays-in-green-nods-by-environment-minister-jayanthi-natarajan%2Farticleshow%2F18438096.cms%5C%22%3Ewas%20also%20presented%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fed-attaches-15-properties-of-a-raja-under-pmla-act%2Farticle67404846.ece%5C%22%3Eas%20corrupt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20successive%20ministers%20taking%20bribes%20to%20clear%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20fix%20these%20problems%2C%20the%20country%20needed%20to%20insulate%20project%20approvals%20from%20inefficiency%20and%20political%20interference.%20One%20solution%20was%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fpolicy%2Fenvironment-clearance-as-patronage%2Farticleshow%2Fmsid-5434996%2Ccurpg-2.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ea%20statutory%20environment%20regulator%20like%20America%E2%80%99s%20Environment%20Protection%20Agency%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20would%20also%20do%20away%20with%20politicians%E2%80%99%20power%20to%20issue%20environment%2Fforest%20clearances.%20This%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%20Instead%2C%20successive%20governments%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.article-14.com%2Fpost%2Findia-is-back-to-a-time-before-the-bhopal-gas-tragedy%5C%22%3Eweakened%20India%E2%80%99s%20environmental%20clearance%20process%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Public%20hearings%20were%20defanged%3B%20project%20proponents%20were%20allowed%20to%20define%20the%20environmental%20parameters%20along%20which%20their%20projects%20would%20be%20evaluated%3B%20the%20time%20taken%20to%20evaluate%20projects%20was%20slashed%3B%20one%20could%20go%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chickens%20are%20now%20coming%20home%20to%20roost.%20In%20both%20Teesta%20III%20and%20Silkyara%2C%20policy%20plans%20and%20project%20reports%20barely%20acknowledged%20environmental%20risks.%20In%20the%20first%20instance%2C%20the%20environmental%20impact%20assessment%20was%20cursory.%20In%20the%20second%2C%20there%20was%20no%20environmental%20impact%20assessment%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20cases%2C%20geological%20risks%20showed%20up%20during%20construction.%20All%20of%20this%20raises%20a%20large%20question.%20Over%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20new%20double%20movement%20of%20fresh%20infrastructure%20projects%20(river-interlinking%2C%20inland%20waterways%2C%20more%20highways%E2%80%A6)%20while%20continuing%20to%20weaken%20India%E2%80%99s%20environmental%20laws.%20The%20resulting%20interplay%20%E2%80%93%20between%20disregarded%20environmental%20risks%20and%20infrastructure%20projects%20%E2%80%93%20has%20to%20be%20better%20understood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragedy%20here%20is%20that%20the%20resulting%20costs%20are%20unfairly%20distributed.%20At%20Silkyara%2C%2041%20workers%20came%20close%20to%20losing%20their%20lives.%20In%20the%20days%20after%20Teesta%20III%E2%80%99s%20collapse%2C%20social%20media%20was%20filled%20with%20images%20of%20locals%20trying%20to%20save%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%2C%20however%2C%20are%20highly%20visible%20instances%20of%20planning%20failures.%20Others%20are%20more%20invisible.%20Poorly%20scrutinised%20risks%20result%20in%20cost-%20and%20time%20overruns%2C%20turning%20projects%20unviable%2C%20even%20forcing%20states%20to%20support%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20are%20the%20costs%20of%20looking%20at%20environmental%20protections%20as%20barriers%20for%