%20an%20opportunity%20to%20spend%20hours%20with%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalled%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20began%20the%20hunt%20for%20games%20and%20toys%20that%20not%20only%20helped%20him%20bond%20with%20his%20daughter%20but%20also%20contributed%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F59319%2Fharsh-songra-my-child-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecognitive%20development%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20this%20search%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20not%20only%20are%20these%20toys%20and%20games%20hard%20to%20find%2C%20but%20they%20can%20also%20burn%20a%20hole%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20realisation%20was%20that%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20make%20toys%20eco-friendly.%20There%20is%20some%20amount%20of%20plastic%20always%20present%20and%20it%20is%20harmful%20to%20the%20environment%20and%20the%20little%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20aspired%20to%20give%20his%20daughter%20the%20world%2C%20he%20also%20endeavoured%20to%20leave%20behind%20a%20cleaner%2C%20greener%2C%20and%20more%20sustainable%20world%20for%20her.%20Today%2C%20he%20owns%20The%20EleFant%20%E2%80%94%20a%20toy%20rental%20company%2C%20or%20in%20Sourabh%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98a%20labour%20of%20love%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20major%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Indore%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20etc.%20Curious%20about%20how%20the%20business%20works%20and%20how%20you%20can%20rent%20toys%20for%20your%20kids%3F%20Read%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainable%2C%20age-appropriate%20and%20fun%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20business%20family%2C%20Sourabh%20always%20had%20an%20entrepreneurial%20mindset.%20Despite%20working%20as%20a%20chartered%20accountant%20for%20most%20of%20his%20life%2C%20he%20harboured%20a%20persistent%20interest%20in%20starting%20his%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20for%20EleFant%20emerged%20from%20the%20desire%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20toys%20for%20my%20daughter%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20brand%20for%20parents%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20business%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20cities%20so%20far.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334717%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20business%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20cities%20so%20far.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20The%20EleFant%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20changing%20family%20dynamics%2C%20Sourabh%20observed%20the%20increasing%20challenge%20for%20parents%20who%20juggle%20work%20and%20home%20responsibilities%20simultaneously.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20time%2C%20I%20would%20be%20working%2C%20leaving%20little%20room%20to%20go%20out%20and%20search%20for%20toys.%20I%20wanted%20to%20simplify%20one%20thing%20for%20working%20parents%20like%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20from%20the%20corporate%20world%20for%20Sourabh%20was%20gradual.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20began%20taking%20shape%20in%20my%20mind%20in%202022%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20a%20solid%20plan%20of%20action.%20I%20aimed%20to%20offer%20parents%20a%20reliable%20service%20and%20an%20effective%20subscription%20model%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESourabh%20also%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20ensuring%20that%20the%20toys%20provided%20to%20children%20are%20not%20just%20enjoyable%20but%20also%20engaging%20and%20educational.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20parent%2C%20I%20understand%20how%20crucial%20it%20is%20for%20kids%20to%20have%20the%20right%20environment%20at%20the%20right%20time%20to%20encourage%20them%20and%20help%20them%20grow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20pursuit%20of%20this%20concept%2C%20Sourabh%20enlisted%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173434%2Fkerala-free-mental-health-care-doctor-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpertise%20of%20a%20psychologist%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20paediatrician%20and%20an%20ex-school%20principal%20to%20discern%20the%20types%20of%20toys%20that%20would%20be%20most%20beneficial%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20nearly%20a%20year%20of%20developing%20the%20concept%20and%20ensuring%20that%20all%20our%20toys%20meet%20the%20highest%20quality%20standards%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20launch%20the%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20company%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20of%20more%20than%20250%20subscribers%20with%20over%202%2C000%20downloads%20of%20the%20application%20per%20day.%20They%20also%20have%20collaborations%20with%2070%20toy%20companies%20where%20they%20source%20their%20toys.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20these%20250%20subscribers%20is%20Rahul%20Bhauwala%20from%20Mum